*****************************************************************************

You have installed the turck-mmcache package.

Edit %%LOCALBASE%%/etc/php.ini and add:

[mmcache]
zend_extension="%%PREFIX%%/lib/php/%%PHP_EXT_DIR%%/mmcache.so"
mmcache.shm_size="16"
mmcache.cache_dir="/tmp"
mmcache.enable="1"
mmcache.optimizer="1"
mmcache.check_mtime="1"
mmcache.debug="0"
mmcache.filter=""
mmcache.shm_max="0"
mmcache.shm_ttl="0"
mmcache.shm_prune_period="0"
mmcache.compress="1"

*****************************************************************************
